## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The psychological and cultural factors influencing the attraction to violent movies are complex and multifaceted, and individual experiences may vary widely. Additionally, the data is limited to studies and articles available up to October 2023, and newer research may provide further insights.

